## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/Vehicle-Counting-System-Using-Python.git
cd Vehicle-Counting-System-Using-Python

2️⃣ Create Virtual Environment (Recommended)
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows

3️⃣ Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

📥 Download Required Files
🔹 YOLO Model

Download the YOLO model file manually:

https://github.com/ultralytics/assets/releases

Place it in the project root:

yolov8n.pt

🔹 Input Video

Add your input video:

video.mp4


(These files are ignored in GitHub for size reasons.)

▶️ How to Run
python app.py

